CORE FEATURES
    - Group Edits
    - Add permissions for new directories
    - Definition of "owners"
    - Loading and saving on server

USABILITY
    - Retrieve directory information using the directory lister
    - Change definition of (real) in directory tree from "existing" to "has permissions defined"
      (therefore also refresh the directory tree when permissions changed)
    - Retrieve fullname of users already in the permissions list
    - Multiselect in lists


AESTHETICS
    - Sorting of user/group lists
    - Add icons to directory tree
    - Styling (a logo!)


DEPLOYMENT
    - Configuration
    - Setup wizard
